@startuml class_diagram

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Calculator {
    .. Binary Arithmetic ..
    + add(a: int|float, b: int|float) : int|float
    + subtract(a: int|float, b: int|float) : int|float
    + multiply(a: int|float, b: int|float) : int|float
    + divide(a: int|float, b: int|float) : float
    .. Unary Algebraic ..
    + square(x: int|float) : int|float
    + cube(x: int|float) : int|float
    + square_root(x: int|float) : float
    + cube_root(x: int|float) : float
    .. Binary Power ..
    + power(base: int|float, exponent: int|float) : int|float
    .. Unary Logarithm ..
    + log10(x: int|float) : float
    + ln(x: int|float) : float
    .. Unary Special ..
    + factorial(n: int) : int
}

note right of Calculator::divide
  raises ZeroDivisionError
  when b == 0
end note

class "calculator()" as fixture <<fixture>> {
    + returns: Calculator
}

class TestCalculatorAdd <<test>> {
    + test_addition_positive_integers()
    + test_addition_negative_integers()
    + test_addition_mixed_signs()
    + test_addition_with_floats()
    + test_addition_with_zero()
    + test_addition_zero_to_zero()
}

class TestCalculatorSubtract <<test>> {
    + test_subtraction_positive_integers()
    + test_subtraction_negative_result()
    + test_subtraction_negative_operands()
    + test_subtraction_with_floats()
    + test_subtraction_with_zero_minuend()
    + test_subtraction_with_zero_subtrahend()
}

class TestCalculatorMultiply <<test>> {
    + test_multiplication_positive_integers()
    + test_multiplication_negative_integers()
    + test_multiplication_mixed_signs()
    + test_multiplication_with_floats()
    + test_multiplication_by_zero()
    + test_multiplication_by_one()
}

class TestCalculatorDivide <<test>> {
    + test_division_by_zero()
    + test_division_normal()
    + test_division_with_floats()
    + test_division_negative_divisor()
    + test_division_zero_dividend()
}

fixture ..> Calculator : instantiates

TestCalculatorAdd ..> fixture : uses
TestCalculatorSubtract ..> fixture : uses
TestCalculatorMultiply ..> fixture : uses
TestCalculatorDivide ..> fixture : uses

TestCalculatorAdd ..> Calculator : invokes add()
TestCalculatorSubtract ..> Calculator : invokes subtract()
TestCalculatorMultiply ..> Calculator : invokes multiply()
TestCalculatorDivide ..> Calculator : invokes divide()

@enduml
